0Mr%20Maken%20explained%20that%20they%20chose%20not%20to%20disclose%20the%20information%20earlier%20as%20the%20hearing%20is%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20learned%20about%20the%20freezing%20of%20its%20accounts%20yesterday%2C%20and%20the%20party's%20lawyer%20Vivek%20Tankha%20said%20that%20a%20total%20of%20four%20accounts%20have%20been%20affected.%20Banks%20have%20been%20instructed%20not%20to%20accept%20or%20honour%20Congress'%20cheques%2C%20with%20the%20frozen%20funds%20to%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Maken%20claimed%20that%20in%20the%20election%20year%20of%202018-19%2C%20the%20party%20submitted%20its%20accounts%2045%20days%20late%2C%20but%20freezing%20the%20accounts%20is%20an%20extreme%20measure.%20He%20argued%20that%20there%20have%20been%20cases%20and%20precedents%20where%20such%20actions%20were%20not%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20given%20the%20names%20of%20all%20MLAs%20and%20MPs%20who%20have%20contributed%2C%20based%20on%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20committee%20report%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Maken%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20claimed%20that%20timing%20of%20the%20freeze%2C%20coming%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20crucial%20general%20elections%2C%20raises%20suspicions%20about%20the%20motives%20behind%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department's%20actions%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20we%20have%20no%20money%20to%20spend.%20Electricity%20bills%2C%20staff%20salaries%2C%20our%20Nyay%20yatra%2C%20everything%20is%20impacted.%20Look%20at%20the%20timing%3B%20this%20is%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20have%20only%20one%20PAN%2C%20and%20the%20four%20accounts%20are%20all%20linked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20voiced%20his%20apprehension%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BIntoxicated%20with%20power%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20frozen%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20opposition%20part