alUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Frashmika-mandanna-to-zepto-founders-heres-2024-forbes-india-list-of-30-under-30-5067639%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Frashmika-mandanna-to-zepto-founders-heres-2024-forbes-india-list-of-30-under-30-5067639%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Frashmika-mandanna-to-zepto-founders-heres-2024-forbes-india-list-of-30-under-30-5067639%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20SRK's%20son%20Abram%20was%20disturbed%20by%20Kajol%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708060337000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107742076%2Cimgsize-65626.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-shah-rukh-khan-said-his-son-abram-was-disturbed-by-kajol-on-the-sets-of-dilwale-papa-toot-gaye%2Farticleshow%2F107742079.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107742079.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20had%20recalled%20a%20cute%20and%20funny%20incident%20from%20the%20sets%20of%20Rohit%20Shetty's%20'Dilwale'%20when%20his%20son%20Abram%20was%20present%20during%20a%20scene%20where%20SRK%20was%20hurt.%20He%20thought%20it%20was%20because%20of%20Kajol%20and%20got%20disturbed!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-shah-rukh-khan-said-his-son-abram-was-disturbed-by-kajol-on-the-sets-of-dilwale-papa-toot-gaye%2Farticleshow%2F107742079.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIT-D%20student%20found%20hanging%20in%20hostel%20room%2C%20suicide%20suspected%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708060285000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107742082%2Cimgsize-80938.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fiit-delhi-student-found-hanging-in-hostel-room-suicide-suspected%2Farticleshow%2F107741801.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2024-year-old%20M.Tech%20student%20at%20IIT%20Delhi%20was%20found%20dead%20by%20hanging%20in%20his%20hostel%20room%2C%20suggesting%20a%20possible%20suicide.%20Concern%20arose%20when%20he%20failed%20to%20answer%20calls%2C%20leading%20hostel%20mates%20to%20investigate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fiit-delhi-student-found-hanging-in-hostel-room-suicide-suspected%2Farticleshow%2F107741801.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO's%20%26quot%3BNaughty%20Boy%26quot%3B%20To%20Launch%20India's%20Latest%20Weather%20Satellite%20Tomorrow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20India%20launches%20its%20latest%20weather%20satellite%20on%20Saturday%2C%20it%20will%20be%20using%20a%20rocket%20that%20has%20been%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3Bnaughty%20boy%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Indian%20space%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Geosynchronous%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(GSLV)%2C%20which%20is%20scheduled%20to%20lift%20off%20with%20the%20INSAT-3DS%20satellite%20from%20Sriharikota%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20at%205.35%20pm%20on%20Saturday%2C%20was%20called%20%26quot%3Bnaughty%20boy%26quot%3B%20by%20a%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20since%20the%20rocket%20has%20not%20performed%20adequately%20in%20six%20of%20its%2015%20flights%20-%20a%20failure%20rate%20of%2040%20per%20cent.%20The%20last%20launch%20of%20the%20GSLV%2C%20on%20May%2029%2C%202023%2C%20was%20successful%20but%20the%20one%20before%20that%20%C2%A0-%20on%20August%2012%2C%202021%20-%20was%20a%20failure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20GSLV's%20heavier%20cousin%2C%20the%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark-3%20or%20the%20'Bahubali%20rocket'%2C%20has%20completed%20seven%20flights%20and%20has%20a%20cent-percent%20success%20record.%20The%20workhorse%20rocket%20of%20ISRO%2C%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV)%2C%20also%20has%20an%20enviable%2095%20per%20cent%20success%20rate%2C%20with%20just%20three%20failures%20in%2060%20launches.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20GSLV%20is%20a%20three-stage%20rocket%20that%20is%2051.7%20metres%20long%20-%20about%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20length%20of%20the%20Statue%20of%20Unity%2C%20which%20stands%20182%20metres%20tall%20-%20and%20has%20a%20liftoff%20mass%20of%20420%20tonnes.%20The%20rocket%20uses%20an%20India-made%20cryogenic%20engine%20and%20ISRO%20plans%20to%20retire%20it%20after%20a%20few%20more%20launches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20satellite%20being%20launched%20on%20Saturday%20is%20very%20special%20and%20is%20much%20needed%20as%20it%20will%20help%20boost%20India's%20weather%20and%20climate%20monitoring%20services.%20Called%20INSAT-3DS%2C%20it%20is%20a%20third-generation%20upgraded%2C%20dedicated%20meteorological%20satellite.%20The%20satellite%20weighs%202%2C274%20kg%20and%20has%20been%20built%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20about%20Rs%20480%20crore.%20It%20is%20fully%20funded%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Earth%20Sciences%2C%20said%20ISRO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Space%20can%20now%20only%20fly%20missions%20that%20are%20fully%20endorsed%20and%20supported%20by%20user%20agencies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBetter%20Forecasts%2C%20Saving%20Lives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20officials%20said%20the%20new%20weather%20monitoring%20satellite%20is%20designed%20for%20enhanced%20meteorological%20observations%20and%20monitoring%20of%20land%20and%20ocean%20surfaces%20for%20weather%20forecasting%20and%20disaster%20warning.%20India%20has%20been%20using%20these%20eyes%20in%20the%20sky%20to%20help%20its%20weather%20office%20give%20increasingly%20accurate%20forecasts%2C%20which%20often%20help%20save%20lives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndian%20weather%20satellites%20have%20been%20a%20game%20changer.%20Satellites%20are%20truly%20the%20eyes%20in%20the%20sky%20that%20have%20helped%20India%20forecast%20cyclones%20with%20great%20precision%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20M%20Ravichandran%2C%20an%20accomplished%20atmosphere%20and%20ocean%20science%20specialist%2C%20who%20is%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Earth%20Sciences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCyclones%20that%20originated%20in%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20during%20the%201970s%20led%20to%20fatalities%20of%20the%20order%20of%20300%2C000%20people.%20But%20this%20was%20before%20the%20Indian%20weather%20satellites%20came%20into%20existence.%20Now%2C%20with%20India%20using%20its%20own%20dedicated%20constellation%20of%20satellites%2C%20the%20cyclone%20forecast%20is%20so%20accurate%20that%20the%20death%20toll%20has%20dropped%20to%20double%20digits%20or%2C%20sometimes%2C%20to%20none%20at%20all.'%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20currently%20has%20three%20operational%20weather%20satellites%3A%20INSAT-3D%2C%20INSAT-3DR%2C%20and%20OceanSat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ashim%20Kumar%20Mitra%2C%20project%20director%20of%20the%20Satellite%20Meteorology%20Division%2C%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BINSAT-3D%20is%20nearing%20its%20end-of-life%20period%20after%20having%20served%20since%202013%2C%20hence%20a%20replacement%20satellite%20was%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20weather%20satellites%20give%20data%20for%20forecasts%2C%20Dr%20Mitra%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSatellites%20basically%20measure%20the%20radiance%20coming%20from%20the%20Earth's%20surface%20and%20cloud%20tops.%20By%20making%20such%20measurements%20at%20appropriate%20wavelengths%20and%20applying%20physical%20and%20statistical%20techniques%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20compute%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products%20for%20weather%20monitoring%20and%20forecasting.%20Further%2C%20the%20satellite%20meteorological%20data%20on%20a%20global%20scale%20are%20vital%20inputs%20in%20Numerical%20Weather%20Prediction%20(NWP)%20models%20as%20initial%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20tropical%20country%20like%20India%20where%20high-impact%20convective%20events%20are%20very%20common%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20have%20good%20quality%2C%20high-density%20observations%20both%20on%20the%20spatial%20and%20temporal%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20satellite%20also%20has%20a%20search-and-rescue%20transponder%20that%20helps%20pick%20distress%20signals%20from%20special%20equipment%20that%20is%20often%20carried%20by%20ships%20and%20even%20trekkers%2C%20helping%20locate%20them%20if%20they%20are%20lost%20in%20remote%20places%20or%20in%20distress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20being%20a%20tropical%20country%20where%20atmospheric%20variations%20are%20high%2C%20weather%20satellites%20are%20an%20essential%20tool%20for%20the%20IMD.%20%26quot%3BAll%20investments%20made%20in%20the%20Indian%20weather%20satellites%20have%20been%20paid%20back%20manifold%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ravichandran%20asserted.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20India%20has%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20if%20the%20%26quot%3Bnaughty%20boy%26quot%3B%20of%20ISRO%20has%20been%20duly%20tamed%20into%20obedience%20or%20it%20continues%20to%20be%20'misbehaved'.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708060080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Feqmmdehg_isro-gslv-insat3ds_625x300_15_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finsat-3ds-launch-isros-naughty-boy-to-launch-indias-latest-weather-satellite-tomorrow-5062882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20India%20launches%20its%20latest%20weather%20satellite%20on%20