t%20remains%20befuddling%20is%20the%20hybrid%20medium%20%E2%80%93%20where%20filmmakers%20interview%20the%20real-life%20couples%20and%20their%20next%20of%20kin%2C%20but%20shoot%20scenes%20reconstructing%20the%20anecdotes%20using%20lookalike%20actors%2C%20with%20the%20real-life%20person%E2%80%99s%20voiceover%20in%20the%20background.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20theory%2C%20I%20think%20I%20can%20see%20what%20the%20filmmakers%20are%20going%20for%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20choices%20are%20not%20quite%20as%20seamless%20as%20one%20might%20imagine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20hurts%20the%20six-episode%20show%20is%20its%20brisk%2025-35%20minutes%20runtime%20per%20episode%20(quite%20possibly%20prescribed%20by%20the%20streaming%20service%20to%20make%20the%20series%20as%20%E2%80%98bingeable%E2%80%99%20as%20possible)%20which%20results%20in%20complex%20issues%20being%20magically%20resolved%20or%20narrative%20lighthouses%20appearing%20out%20of%20nowhere%20and%20oversimplifying%20the%20challenges%20of%20relationships%20spanning%20decades%20into%20bite-sized%20pieces%20of%20%E2%80%98content%E2%80%99%2C%20so%20it%20can%20be%20described%20as%20%E2%80%98wholesome%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Which%20again%2C%20is%20not%20to%20say%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELove%20Storiyaan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20an%20insincere%20show.%20It%E2%80%99s%20fully%20aware%20that%20by%20releasing%20in%20a%20time%20when%20conforming%20is%20the%20rule%2C%20merely%20endorsing%20these%20trailblazers%20is%20a%20political%20act.%20Most%20of%20these%20episodes%20here%2C%20despite%20some%20stretches%20of%20dubious%20craft%2C%20ensure%20they%20end%20up%20as%20cathartic%20at%20least%20%E2%80%93%20a%20solid%20starting%20point.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FaH48GzdWn0I%3Fsi%3DUWJkouH9LY77yvoY%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EAn%20Unsuitable%20Girl%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDirected%20by%20Hardik%20Mehta%2C%20who%20has%20shown%20a%20wild%20range%20of%20temperaments%20from%20his%20breakout%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAmdavad%20Ma%20Famous%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2015)%20to%20Netflix%20series%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDecoupled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2021)%2C%20this%20episode%20is%20an%20urban%20Bollywood%20rom-com%20setup.%20Aekta%2C%20a%2033-year-old%20writer%2Feditor%20based%20in%20Delhi%2C%20meets%20Ullekh%20%E2%80%93%20a%20journalist%20based%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20old-fashioned%20online%20way.%20In%20the%20comments%20section%20of%20her%20lifestyle%20blog.%20The%20conflict%20arises%20when%20Aekta%E2%80%99s%20two%20daughters%20from%20her%20first%20marriage%20have%20to%20approve%20of%20their%20mother%E2%80%99s%20partner%20before%20they%20can%20take%20it%20forward.%20The%20way%20Mehta%20reconstructs%20it%20using%20actors%2C%20I%20could%20imagine%20Manav%20Kaul%20and%20Shefali%20Shah%20playing%20Ullekh%20and%20Aekta%20in%20a%20fictitious%20version%20of%20this%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20strongest%20bit%20of%20this%20episode%20is%20Aekta%20confessing%20to%20discovering%20her%20self-worth%20in%20her%20job%20as%20a%20writer%2Feditor%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98light%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20dark%2C%20lonely%20marriage.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20playfulness%20to%20the%20story%20which%20makes%20it%20ripe%20for%20a%20Bollywood%20adaptation.%20Mehta%20employs%20that%20in%20a%20reconstruction%20scene%2C%20like%20one%20of%20Aekta%E2%80%99s%20daughters%20showing%20her%20hostility%20to%20Ullekh%20in%20a%20sweet%2C%20savage%20manner.%20The%20story%20is%20all%20trumps%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccuteness%E2%80%9D%20of%20it%20is%20all%20that%20remains%20in%20the%20end%2C%20overcoming%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20stagey%20craft.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELove%20On%20Air%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Northeast%20has%20always%20been%20a%20tricky%20place%20for%20Hindi%20films%2C%20and%20the%20cultural%20awkwardness%20continues%20in%20Vivek%20Soni%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELove%20On%20Air%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20following%20two%20rival%20radio%20jockeys%20falling%20in%20love%20in%20Meghalaya.%20Soni%E2%80%99s%20directorial%20debut%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMeenakshi%20Sundareshwar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20infamous%20for%20Hindi-fying%20Madurai%2C%20and%20here%20you%20see%20him%20trying%20to%20be%20more%20cognisant%20of%20the%20fact%20with%20Nicholas%20and%20Rajani%E2%80%99s%20love%20story.%20However%2C%20the%20gaze%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20outsider%E2%80%99s%2C%20with%20hints%20of%20exoticisation%20most%20visible%20in%20a%20voice-over%20straight%20out%20of%20Bollywood.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENicholas%20is%20a%20Christian%20man%2C%20divorced%2C%20playing%20up%20the%20facade%20of%20a%20casanova%20(he%20brags%20about%20how%20he%20would%20go%20on%20multiple%20dates%20every%20week)%2C%20which%20is%20a%20way%20to%20mask%20his%20drinking%20problem.%20Rajani%2C%20a%20headstrong%2C%20Hindu%20woman%2C%20in%20a%20steady%20relationship%20when%20she%20meets%20Nicholas%2C%20slowly%20begins%20to%20embrace%20the%20ease%20she%20feels%20around%20him.%20The%20surprise%20package%20of%20this%20segment%20is%20their%20cupid%20%E2%80%93%20Mandira%2C%20a%20devoted%2C%20visually-impaired%20listener%20for%20both%20Nick%20and%20Rajani%E2%80%99s%20programmes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20inter-faith%20couple%20comes%20together%20despite%20opposition%20from%20her%20parents%2C%20and%20talks%20about%20how%20the%20%E2%80%98fairytale%E2%80%99%20was%20tested%20during%20Nicholas%E2%80%99%20periods%20of%20alcohol%20addiction.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20sombre%20moment%20that%20grounds%20the%20episode.%20When%20Nicholas%2C%20Rajani%20and%20their%20son%20Mahyaan%20pay%20a%20surprise%20visit%20to%20Mandira%20%E2%80%93%20a%20tearful%20reunion%20worthy%20of%20cameras%20%E2%80%93%20to%20Soni%E2%80%99s%20credit%2C%20he%20keeps%20rolling%20after%20they%20leave.%20After%20promising%20to%20%E2%80%98stay%20in%20touch%E2%80%99%2C%20Soni%20films%20the%20loneliness%20in%20Mandira%E2%80%99s%20life.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20touching%20ode%20to%20those%20who%20magnanimously%20bat%20for%20love%2C%20even%20if%20they%20only%20have%20their%20solitude%20to%20live%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103131%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.29.32%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x457.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103131%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.29.32%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x457.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103131%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.29.32%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x134.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103131%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.29.32%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697434%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22375%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Love%20Storiyaan%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHomecoming%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShazia%20Iqbal%E2%80%99s%20episode%20about%20a%20Hindu-Muslim%20couple%20eloping%20from%20Dhaka%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20in%20search%20of%20their%20happily-ever-after%20in%20Kolkata%20%E2%80%93%20is%20one%20of%20the%