n.%20We%20want%20solution%2C%20not%20confrontation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20convener%20of%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(non-%20political)%2C%20which%20is%20leading%20the%20protests%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20while%20farmers%20were%20fully%20determined%20to%20march%20to%20Delhi%2C%20they%20would%20wait%20for%20the%20outcome%20of%20Sunday%E2%80%99s%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20talks%20fail%20on%20that%20day%2C%20we%20will%20go%20ahead.%20But%20till%20that%20time%20we%20will%20maintain%20status%20quo%20and%20expect%20security%20forces%20to%20adopt%20restraint%20and%20avoid%20any%20shelling%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20barrier%20where%20our%20farmers%20are%20camping%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-at-shambhu-barrier-vow-not-to-return-until-centre-enacts-a-law-on-msp%5C%22%3EFarmers%20at%20Shambhu%20Barrier%20Vow%20Not%20to%20Return%20Until%20Centre%20Enacts%20a%20Law%20on%20MSP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20chief%20minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%2C%20who%20was%20also%20present%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20also%20raised%20the%20matter%20on%20the%20suspension%20of%20internet%20in%20three%20districts%20of%20Punjab%20bordering%20Haryana%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20caused%20problems%20for%20students%20who%20had%20to%20write%20exams%20and%20affected%20normal%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMann%20said%20such%20a%20move%20was%20not%20necessary%20when%20farmers%20were%20camping%20peacefully.%20He%20asked%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20restore%20the%20internet%20since%20talks%20were%20progressing%20in%20a%20positive%20direction%2C%20his%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%20Union%20agriculture%20minister%20Arjun%20Munda%2C%20who%20represented%20the%20Union%20government%20along%20with%20commerce%20minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20and%20junior%20home%20minister%2C%20Nityanand%20Rai%2C%20did%20not%20say%20much%20except%20that%20the%20talks%20were%20held%20in%20a%20positive%20atmosphere.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20were%20working%20for%20peaceful%20resolution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Munda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20several%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%2C%20including%20SKM%20splinter%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20other%20than%20those%20camping%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders%20%E2%80%93%20have%20called%20for%20a%20Gramin%20Bharat%20Bandh%20today%2C%20to%20press%20for%20their%20demands%20before%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20the%20call%20is%20already%20seen%20in%20Punjab%20as%20government%20and%20private%20buses%20operators%20will%20pause%20operations.%20The%20Punjab%20Petrol%20Dealers%20Association%20too%20has%20supported%20the%20call%20and%20decided%20to%20close%20fuel%20stations%20in%20the%20state.%20All%20agriculture%20and%20commercial%20activities%20are%20expected%20to%20cease.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708056074000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16091726%2FIMG_20240215_150214_364-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-meeting-union-government%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20government%20has%20sought%20another%20round%20of%20meetings%20on%20Sunday%2C%20February%2018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-meeting-union-government%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%229%20Los%20Angeles%20firefighters%20injured%20in%20explosion%20of%20burning%20truck's%20fuel%20tank%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708055691000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107740078%2Cimgsize-243268.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2F9-los-angeles-firefighters-injured-in-explosion-of-burning-trucks-fuel-tank%2Fa