in-recent-history-un-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F107739808.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fterror-groups-enjoy-greater-freedom-in-afghanistan-than-at-any-time-in-recent-history-un-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F107739808.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sandeshkhali%20Case%20In%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Probe%20Sought%20In%20Sex%20Harassment%20Charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Sandeshkhali%20case%20from%20West%20Bengal%2C%20centered%20around%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20and%20land%20grabbing%20by%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20leader%2C%20has%20now%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20after%20sparking%20nationwide%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Alakh%20Alok%20Srivastava%20has%20filed%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20urging%20an%20impartial%20investigation%20by%20either%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20or%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20into%20the%20allegations.%20The%20petition%20not%20only%20seeks%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20the%20responsible%20police%20officers%20but%20also%20demands%20compensation%20for%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20alleged%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turmoil%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20began%20on%20January%205%2C%20following%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20raid%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20Trinamool%20strongman%20Shajahan%20Shiekh%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20multi-crore%20ration%20distribution%20scam.%20Shajahan's%20men%20reportedly%20assaulted%20ED%20officers%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20chaotic%20situation%20that%20has%20since%20snowballed%20in%20a%20political%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20came%20forward%20with%20allegations%20of%20land%20grabbing%20and%20years%20of%20torture%20and%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20women%20alleged%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20leaders%20would%20torture%20them.%20%26quot%3BThey%20targeted%20women%20by%20picking%20up%20their%20husbands%20and%20beating%20them%20up%20with%20a%20stick%20in%20the%20party%20office.%20If%20we%20refused%20to%20go%20to%20the%20party%20office%2C%20they%20would%20pick%20up%20the%20men%20and%20thrash%20them%20so%20we%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20targeted%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20allegations.%20The%20ruling%20party%20has%20trashed%20the%20charges%20and%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20unrest%20in%20the%20area.%20There%20have%20been%20several%20incidents%20of%20violence%20in%20the%20region%20around%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%2C%20after%20a%20visit%20to%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20described%20the%20situation%20as%20%26quot%3Bghastly%2C%20shocking%2C%20shattering%26quot%3B%20and%20submitted%20a%20report%20blaming%20law%20enforcement%20for%20collaborating%20with%20%26quot%3Browdy%20elements%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20area.%20He%20suggested%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20Special%20Task%20Force%20to%20probe%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708055460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F0qlpkdl4_sandeshkhali_625x300_16_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsandeshkhali-case-in-supreme-court-probe-sought-into-sex-harassment-charges-5067293%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Sandeshkhali%20case%20from%20West%20Bengal%2C%20centered%20around%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20and%20land%20grabbing%20by%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20leader%2C%20has%20now%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20after%20sparking%20nationwide%20outrage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsandeshkhali-case-in-supreme-court-probe-sought-into-sex-harassment-charge