h%20unbeaten%20centurion%20Ravindra%20Jadeja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2026-year-old%20was%2C%20however%2C%20too%20happy%20to%20have%20any%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComing%20to%20the%20ground%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20getting%20the%20cap%20in%20front%20of%20my%20father.%20I%20was%20six%20years%20old%20when%20he%20started%20my%20cricket%20(training).%20It%20was%20my%20dream%20to%20play%20for%20the%20Indian%20team%20in%20front%20of%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarfaraz%20told%20the%20media%20here%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day's%20play%20in%20which%20India%20were%20326%2F5.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Test%20cap%20No%20311%2C%20Sarfaraz%20gave%20a%20fine%20account%20of%20himself%20with%20a%20rapid%2062.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaushad%20was%20overwhelmed%20on%20Thursday.%20He%20had%20not%20even%20planned%20to%20visit%20Rajkot%20to%20watch%20his%20son%20but%20landed%20in%20the%20city%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETears%2C%20hugs%20and%20joy%20swept%20through%20the%20Khan%20family%20with%20Sarfaraz's%20wife%20present%20beside%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20padded%20up%20for%20almost%20four%20hours%20(in%20the%20dressing%20room).%20I%20kept%20thinking%20that%20I%20have%20kept%20so%20much%20patience%20in%20life%20and%20there%20is%20no%20harm%20in%20keeping%20some%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20I%20went%20in%2C%20I%20was%20nervous%20for%20the%20first%20few%20balls%20but%20I%20have%20practiced%20and%20worked%20so%20hard%20that%20everything%20went%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarfaraz%20said%20detailing%20his%20Test%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%20said%20runs%20and%20performances%20did%20not%20matter%20to%20him%20as%20much%20as%20playing%20for%20India%20with%20his%20father%20there%20to%20watch%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20my%20father's%20dream%20to%20play%20for%20India%20but%20unfortunately%20it%20couldn't%20happen%20due%20to%20some%20reasons%2C%20there%20wasn't%20much%20support%20from%20home%20then.%20He%20worked%20very%20hard%20on%20me%20and%20is%20now%20doing%20the%20same%20with%20my%20brother.%20It%20was%20the%20proudest%20moment%20of%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRuns%20and%20performances%20were%20not%20on%20my%20mind%20as%20much%20as%20I%20was%20happy%20playing%20for%20India%20in%20front%20of%20my%20father%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20not%20ready%20to%20come%20(to%20Rajkot)%20but%20some%20people%20insisted%20that%20he%20goes.%20Obviously%20he%20had%20to%20come%20over%20since%20he%20worked%20so%20hard%20only%20for%20this%20day.%E2%80%9D%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20very%20emotional%20as%20I%20took%20the%20cap%20in%20front%20of%20him%20and%20so%20was%20my%20wife.%20I%20felt%20as%20if%20some%20pressure%20was%20off%20my%20shoulders%20given%20the%20hard%20work%20he%20had%20put%20in%20on%20me%20and%20I%20did%20not%20waste%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated%20emotions%20still%20raw%20after%20a%20whirlwind%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%20banished%20initial%20nervousness%20with%20powerful%20sweeps%20and%20lofted%20hits%20down%20the%20ground%20but%20termed%20his%20dismissal%20--%20the%20run%20out%20at%20the%20non-striker's%20end%20--%20a%20case%20of%20%26quot%3Bmiscommunication%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20game.%20Miscommunication%20happens%20in%20cricket.%20Sometimes%20run-out%20happens%2C%20sometimes%20you%20get%20the%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spoke%20to%20Jadeja%20at%20lunch%20time%20and%20requested%20him%20to%20talk%20to%20me%20while%20playing.%20I%20like%20talking%20while%20playing.%20It%20was%20my%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20told%20him%20that%20when%20I%20go%20out%20to%20bat%2C%20keep%20talking%20to%20me%20while%20playing.%20He%20kept%20talking%20and%20supported%20me%20a%20lot%20while%20I%20was%20batting%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarfaraz%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20easy%20for%20any%20player%20to%20keep%20trudging%20through%20years%20of%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20piling%20up%20runs%20year%20after%20year%20and%20not%20get%20a%20chance%20in%20the%20national%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20finally%20got%20it%2C%20Sarfaraz%20said%20the%20taste%20of%20international%20cricket%20was%20almost%20similar%20to%20domestic%2C%20but%20with%20a%20few%20obvious%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInitially%20I%20was%20feeling%20awkward%20since%20it%20has%20been%20a%20long%20time%20in%20anticipation.%20But%20later%20on%20I%20felt%20that%20I%20have%20done%20all%20of%20this%2C%20once%20I%20was%20in%20my%20zone%20I%20did%20not%20find%20it%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDifference%20is%20there%2C%20you%20do%20not%20have%20crowds%20in%20first-class%20cricket%20and%20you%20do%20not%20come%20across%20national%20players%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708054200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F7nu4a6rg_sarfaraz-khan-father-afp_625x300_15_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Ffather-wanted-to-play-for-india-but-sarfaraz-khans-revelation-after-record-breaking-half-century-on-debut-5064050%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sarfaraz%20Khan%20finally%20made%20his%20much-anticipated%20international%20debut%2C%20entertaining%20the%20spectators%20with%20his%20knock%20of%2062%20in%2066%20balls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A84%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20%26quot%3BWonder%26quot%3B%20Drug%20Offers%20Breakthrough%20In%20Treatment%20Of%20Deadly%20Cancer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EScientists%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20have%20welcomed%20a%20%26quot%3Btruly%20wonderful%26quot%3B%20new%20drug%20for%20a%20hard-to-treat%20and%20aggressive%20form%20of%20cancer.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fscience%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F15%2Fdrug-offers-wonderful-breakthrough-in-treatment-of-asbestos-linked-cancer%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20researchers%20at%20the%20Queen%20Mary%20University%20London%20said%20their%20new%20treatment%20%26quot%3Bquadrupled%26quot%3B%20three-year%20survival%20rates%20and%20increased%20average%20survival%20by%201.6%20months.%20They%20also%20added%20that%20the%20new%20drug%2C%20which%20works%20by%20cutting%20off%20the%20tumour's%20food%20supply%2C%20is%20the%20first%20of%20its%20type%20for%20mesothelioma%20in%2020%20years.%20The%20results%20were%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamaoncology%2Ffullarticle%2F2815000%5C%22%3Ejournal%20JAMA%20Oncology%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMesothelioma%20is%20a%20type%20of%20cancer%20that%20develops%20in%20the%20lungs%20and%20is%20mainly%20caused%20by%20exposure%20to%20asbestos%20at%20work.%20It%20is%20aggressive%20and%20deadly%20and%20has%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20worst%20cancer%20survival%20rates.%20Thousands%20of%20people%20are%20diagnosed%20with%20the%20disease%20globally%20and%20according%20to%20the%20official%20figures%2C%20there%20are%20about%202%2C700%20new%20cases%20of%20mesothelioma%20each%20year%20in%20the%20UK.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20at%20Queen%20Mary%20University%20of%20London%20conducted%20an%20international%20trial%20spanning%20five%20countries%20-%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20Italy%20and%20Taiwan.%20For%20the%20study%2C%20led%20by%20Professor%20Peter%20Szlosarek%20at%20Queen%20Mary%2C%20the%20team%20saw%20all%20patients%20receive%20chemotherapy%20every%20three%20weeks%20for%20up%20to%20six%20cycles.%20Half%20of%20them%20were%20injected%20with%20the%20new%20drug%20ADI-PEG20%20(pegargiminase)%2C%20while%20the%20other%20half%20received%20a%20placebo%20for%20two%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20patients%20included%20in%20the%20final%20analysis%20were%20249%20people%20with%20pleural%20mesothelioma%20-%20when%20the%20disease%20affects%20the%20lining%20of%20the%20lungs.%20They%20had%20an%20average%20age%20of%2070.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ATOMIC-meso%20trial%20was%20conducted%20at%2043%20centres%20across%20five%20countries%20between%202017%20and%202021.%20Patients%20involved%20in%20the%20study%20were%20followed%20up%20for%20at%20least%20a%20year.%20Those%20who%20received%20pegargiminase%20and%20chemotherapy%20survived%20for%20an%20average%20of%209.3%20months%2C%20compared%20to%207.7%20months%20for%20those%20who%20had%20the%20placebo%20and%20chemotherapy%2C%20as%20per%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20%26quot%3Bprogression-free%20survival%26quot%3B%20was%206.2%20months%20with%20pegargiminase-chemotherapy%2C%20compared%20with%205.6%20months%20among%20patients%20who%20had%20the%20placebo%20and%20chemotherapy%2C%20researchers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20pivotal%2C%20randomised%2C%20placebo-controlled%2C%20phase%203%20trial%20in%20249%20patients%20with%20pleural%20mesothelioma%2C%20pegargiminase-chemotherapy%20increased%20significantly%20the%20median%20overall%20survival%20by%201.6%20months%20and%20quadrupled%20the%20survival%20at%2036%20months%20compared%20to%20placebo-chemotherapy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPegargiminase-based%20chemotherapy%20was%20well%20tolerated%2C%20with%20no%20new%20safety%20signals%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fgulf-stream-could-collapse-as-early-as-2025-mini-ice-age-on-the-way-study-5061782%5C%22%3EGulf%20Stream%20Could%20Collapse%20As%20Early%20As%202025%2C%20Mini%20Ice%20Age%20On%20The%20Way%3A%20Study%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20researchers%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20successful%20combination%20of%20chemotherapy%20with%20a%20drug%20that%20targets%20cancer's%20metabolism%20developed%20for%20this%20disease%20in%2020%20years.%20The%20new%20drug%20works%20by%20depleting%20arginine%20levels%20in%20the%20bloodstream.%20For%20tumour%20cells%20that%20cannot%20manufacture%20their%20own%20arginine%2C%20this%20means%20their%20growth%20is%20thwarted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20truly%20wonderful%20to%20see%20the%20research%20into%20the%20arginine%20starvation%20of%20cancer%20cells%20come%20to%20fruition%2C%26quot%3B%20Professor%20Szlosarek%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20discovery%20is%20something%20I%20have%20been%20driving%20from%20its%20earliest%20stages%20in%20the%20lab%2C%20with%20a%20new%20treatment%2C%20ADI-PEG20%2C%20now%20improving%20patient%20lives%20affected%20by%20mesothelioma%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708053960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ftblvcuk_lungs-generic_625x300_16_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fuk-scientists-develop-new-wonder-drug-that-offers-breakthrough-treatment-of-deadly-cancer-5067183%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scientists%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20have%20welcomed%20a%20%26quot%3Btruly%20wonderful%26quot%3B%20new%20drug%20for%20a%20hard-to-treat%20and%20aggressive%20form%20of%20cancer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fuk-scientists-develop-new-wonder-drug-that-offers-breakthrough-treatment-of-deadly-cancer-5067183%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fuk-scientists-develop-new-wonder-drug-that-offers-breakthrough-treatment-of-deadly-cancer-5067183%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUr