be%20disqualified%20from%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20in%20the%20moving%20papers%20supports%20Willis's%20disqualification%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20motion%20should%20have%20been%20dismissed%20out%20of%20hand%20or%20referred%20to%20the%20state%20disciplinary%20committee%20for%20consideration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorman%20Eisen%2C%20an%20attorney%20and%20former%20diplomat%20who%20served%20as%20special%20counsel%20to%20the%20House%20Judiciary%20Committee%20during%20Trump's%20first%20impeachment%20trial%2C%20called%20the%20Thursday%20hearing%20a%20%26quot%3Bspectacle.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20those%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20disqualify%20DA%20Willis%20have%20not%20met%20their%20steep%20burden%20under%20Georgia%20law%20to%20prove%20a%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20Eisen%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225339%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fulton%20County%20DA%20Fani%20Willis%20testifies%20at%20a%20hearing%20Feb.%2015%20in%20Atlanta%20on%20her%20relationship%20with%20Special%20Prosecutor%20Nathan%20Wade.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cebe14f533b039a8845cd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222670%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFulton%20County%20DA%20Fani%20Willis%20testifies%20at%20a%20hearing%20Feb.%2015%20in%20Atlanta%20on%20her%20relationship%20with%20Special%20Prosecutor%20Nathan%20Wade.%3Cp%3EPool%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EToo%20arrogant%20to%20prepare%20to%20testify%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20legal%20experts%2C%20however%2C%20were%20less%20dismissive%20of%20the%20hearing's%20merits%20and%20more%20critical%20of%20Willis'%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20Krissoff%2C%20a%20former%20federal%20prosecutor%20in%20New%20York%2C%20said%20the%20defendants'%20accusations%20are%20not%20%26quot%3Bfrivolous%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20even%20the%20appearance%20of%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20case%20has%20to%20be%20addressed%20because%20of%20the%20national%20importance%20of%20the%20Trump-related%20legal%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20seemed%20to%20be%20dismissing%20it%20and%20not%20taking%20it%20as%20seriously%20as%20it%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Krissoff%20told%20BI%20of%20Willis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20on%20the%20stand%2C%20Willis%20cracked%20jokes%20and%20snapped%20back%20at%20defense%20attorneys%2C%20appearing%20eager%20to%20retake%20control%20of%20the%20case.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20she%20quipped%20to%20a%20lawyer%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20be%20cute%20with%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Bederow%2C%20a%20defense%20attorney%20and%20former%20prosecutor%20in%20the%20Manhattan%20DA's%20office%2C%20called%20Willis'%20and%20Wade's%20testimony%20%26quot%3Ba%20full-fledged%20disaster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20as%20if%20she%20is%20so%20arrogant%2C%20she%20wasn't%20prepared%20to%20testify%2C%26quot%3B%20Bederow%20said%20of%20Willis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20shocked%20by%20the%20former%20couple's%20claims%20that%20Willis%20exclusively%20paid%20Wade%20for%20their%20trips%20with%20large%20amounts%20of%20cash%20she%20said%20she%20regularly%20keeps%20on%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20seasoned%20lawyer%2C%20no%20records%3F%20No%20paper%3F%26quot%3B%20Bederow%20questioned%20of%20Wade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeama%20Rahmani%2C%20a%20former%20federal%20prosecutor%20in%20California%2C%20said%20he%20was%20also%20skeptical%20of%20Willis'%20and%20Wade's%20explanations%20on%20the%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20have%20Venmo%20and%20Zelle.%20She%20said%20she%20never%20Cash%20Apped%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahmani%20said.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20was%20cash%20and%20he%20never%20deposited%20it%3F%20I%20just%20don't%20find%20that%20believable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fulton%20County%20DA%20Fani%20Willis%20testifies%20at%20a%20hearing%20Feb.%2015%20in%20Atlanta%20on%20her%20relationship%20with%20Special%20Prosecutor%20Nathan%20Wade.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cebea1f533b039a8845cd8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFulton%20County%20DA%20Fani%20Willis%20testifies%20at%20a%20hearing%20Feb.%2015%20in%20Atlanta%20on%20her%20relationship%20with%20Special%20Prosecutor%20Nathan%20Wade.%3Cp%3EPool%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWillis%20has%20been%20forced%20to%20go%20on%20the%20defense%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Willis%20reminded%20the%20court%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20people%20are%20on%20trial%20for%20trying%20to%20steal%20an%20election%20in%202020.%20I'm%20not%20on%20trial%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20hard%20you%20try%20to%20put%20me%20on%20trial.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20during%20Thursday's%20hearing%2C%20several%20legal%20experts%20said%20the%20hearing%20is%20unlikely%20to%20affect%20the%20case%20from%20a%20legal%20standpoint.%20Most%20experts%20were%20skeptical%20that%20the%20evidence%20presented%20Thursday%20would%20lead%20to%20Willis%20or%20Wade%20being%20dismissed%20from%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20might%20not%20matter%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20Rahmani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWillis%20came%20out%20swinging%2C%20but%20I%20would%20say%20it's%20too%20little%2C%20too%20late%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BShe%20has%20lost%20the%20PR%20battle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWillis%20waited%20weeks%20to%20address%20the%20allegations%2C%20only%20confirming%20her%20and%20Wade's%20relationship%20in%20a%20filing%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20though%20she%20denied%20any%20financial%20impropriety%20as%20a%20result%20of%20their%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20DA's%20delayed%20response%20time%2C%20coupled%20with%20testimony%20from%20her%20former%20friend%20on%20Thursday%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffani-willis-nathan-wade-testimony-fulton-county-georgia-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtradicted%20Willis'%20claims%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20when%20her%20relationship%20with%20Wade%20actually%20began%2C%20has%20undercut%20Willis'%20control%20of%20the%20case%2C%20Rahmani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20embarrassing%20sideshow.%20She's%20on%20the%20defense%20when%20she%20should%20be%20on%20the%20offense%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahmani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrissoff%20concurred%2C%20saying%20that%20Thursday's%20hearing%20may%20have%20done%20damage%20to%20Willis'%20reputation%20with%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20Willis%20is%20ultimately%20successful%2C%20Trump's%20team%20is%20going%20to%20be%20screaming%20six%20ways%20to%20Sunday%20that%20this%20was%20a%20biased%2C%20flawed%20prosecution%2C%26quot%3B%20Krissoff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20even%20if%20the%20judge%20doesn't%20buy%20that%20argument%2C%20I%20think%20the%20public%20might%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BThat%20might%20be%20a%20constituency%20that's%20more%20important%20than%20the%20judge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20will%20continue%2C%20with%20Willis%20resuming%20testimony%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffani-willis-stand-legal-experts-split-effectiveness-georgia-trump-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708053712000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cec15b6fcb546d2d507cc4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffani-willis-stand-legal-experts-split-effectiveness-georgia-trump-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fani%20Willis%20testified%20Thursday%20about%20her%20relationship%20with%20Nathan%20Wade%2C%20th