bs%2C%20dairy%2C%20and%20some%20meat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20study%20found%20people%20on%20the%20Atlantic%20diet%20had%20a%20lower%20risk%20of%20metabolic%20syndrome%20and%20less%20belly%20fat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20love%20carbs%20and%20want%20to%20eat%20more%20healthfully%2C%20a%20close%20neighbor%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Favoid-most-common-mistakes-following-mediterranean-diet-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20just%20the%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Atlantic%20diet%2C%20based%20on%20traditional%20eating%20habits%20in%20northern%20Spain%20and%20Portugal%2C%20may%20help%20prevent%20chronic%20illness%20and%20promote%20a%20healthy%20metabolism%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20published%20February%207%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamanetworkopen%2Ffullarticle%2F2814624%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJAMA%20Network%20Open%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20new%20research%20suggests%20that%20this%20carb-heavy%2C%20dairy-friendly%20eating%20plan%20may%20have%20similar%20health%20benefits%20to%20the%20much-praised%20Mediterranean%20diet%20in%20protecting%20metabolic%20health%20and%20preventing%20chronic%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Atlantic%20diet%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Atlantic%20diet%20diet%20focuses%20on%20plenty%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-diet-food-list-cheap-easy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elongevity-boosting%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20produce%2C%20olive%20oil%2C%20beans%2C%20seafood%2C%20and%20even%20some%20wine.%20It's%20similar%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmediterrean-diet-healthiest-best-overall-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ranked%20as%20one%20of%20the%20healthiest%20ways%20to%20eat%2C%20emphasizing%20mostly%20unprocessed%20whole%20foods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Atlantic%20diet%20features%20even%20more%20carbs%2C%20specifically%20whole%20grains%20and%20starchy%20foods%20like%20bread%2C%20pasta%2C%20and%20potatoes.%20It%20recommends%20six%20to%20eight%20servings%20of%20these%20a%20day.%20It%20also%20includes%20cheese%20and%20other%20dairy%2C%20along%20with%20lean%20meats%2C%20and%20red%20meat%20in%20moderation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20are%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20Atlantic%20diet%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Santiago%20de%20Compostela%20in%20Spain%20followed%20231%20families%20(including%20518%20people)%20from%20rural%20Spain%20over%20six%20months%2C%20analyzing%20their%20metabolic%20health%20with%20measurements%20like%20their%20weight%2C%20cholesterol%20levels%2C%20and%20blood%20pressure.%20Half%20the%20participants%20were%20randomly%20assigned%20to%20follow%20a%20traditional%20Atlantic%20diet%2C%20and%20provided%20with%20food%2C%20cooking%20classes%2C%20and%20other%20resources%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20other%20half%20were%20instructed%20to%20follow%20their%20habitual%20eating%20patterns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20six%20months%2C%20people%20on%20the%20Atlantic%20diet%20were%2068%25%20less%20likely%20to%20develop%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fmetabolic-syndrome-diet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emetabolic%20syndrome%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20collection%20of%20health%20issues%20like%20risky%20cholesterol%20levels%2C%20that%20can%20increase%20the%20odds%20of%20heart%20disease%2C%20stroke%2C%20or%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20had%20trimmer%20waistlines%20and%20were%20less%20likely%20to%20have%20high%20levels%20of%20belly%20fat%20compared%20to%20their%20peers%20who%20didn't%20follow%20the%20diet%2C%20researchers%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20diet%20didn't%20seem%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20to%20specific%20health%20measures%20like%20blood%20pressure%20or%20blood%20sugar%20levels%2C%20so%20more%20research%20is%20needed%20to%20understand%20how%20it%20works%20and%20who%20could%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20researchers%20did%20find%20that%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20the%20health%20benefits%20was%20participants%20following%20the%20diet%20as%20a%20family.%20Previous%20research%20suggests%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmediterranean-diet-may-make-family-healthier-too-study-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20support%20can%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20create%20healthy%20habits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20maintain%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20there's%20good%20evidence%20that%20eating%20more%20nutrient-dense%20whole%20foods%20has%20a%20wealth%20of%20benefits%20for%20health%20and%20longevity%2C%20whether%20you%20make%20more%20Mediterranean%20meals%2C%20buy%20into%20the%20%26quot%3BBlue%20Zones%26quot%3B%20style%20of%20eating%2C%20or%20opt%20for%20the%20Atlantic%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-atlantic-diet-health-benefits-study-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708038028000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce763ca610a9069d598764%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-atlantic-diet-health-benefits-study-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Atlantic%20diet%20is%20linked%20to%20reduced%20belly%20fat%20and%20lower%20risk%20of%20disease%2C%20and%20it's%20full%20of%20carb-rich%20foods%20like%20bread%20and%20pasta%2C%20new%20research%20suggests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22glandsverk%40insider.com%20(Gabby%20Landsverk)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-atlantic-diet-health-benefits-study-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%2