have%20reached%20out%20on%20the%20topic%2C%20mostly%20asking%20some%20version%20of%20%26quot%3BWTF.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20immediate%20thought%20was%20probably%20the%20same%20as%20most%20people%20when%20I%20heard%20the%20news%3A%20oof%2C%20that's%20a%20really%2C%20really%20bad%20mistake.%20Next%3A%20my%20heart%20broke%20for%20a%20company%20I%20still%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20biggest%20reaction%3F%20It's%20amazing%20that%20something%20like%20this%20doesn't%20happen%20much%20more%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202008%2C%20I've%20held%20the%20pen%20on%2030%2B%20earnings%20scripts%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20Visa%2C%20Pandora%2C%20Lyft%2C%20and%20several%20clients%20at%20Valentine%20Advisors.%20I%20know%20firsthand%20the%20extreme%20level%20of%20complexity%20and%20precision%20required%20to%20birth%20an%20earnings%20report%20every%20three%20months.%20It%20involves%20countless%20hours%20from%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20organization%2C%20including%20top%20execs%2C%20investor%20relations%2C%20finance%2C%20legal%2C%20communications.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20my%20Visa%20days%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20twin%20toddlers%20would%20decamp%20to%20grandma's%20house%20for%20two%20weeks%20because%20we%20knew%20I'd%20be%20fully%20consumed%20with%20the%20earnings%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20%E2%80%94%20amazingly%20%E2%80%94%20the%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20earnings%20cycles%20for%20thousands%20of%20companies%20go%20off%20without%20a%20hitch.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20the%20earnings%20process%20has%20reached%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techtarget.com%2Fsearchnetworking%2Ffeature%2FThe-Holy-Grail-of-five-nines-reliability%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20nines%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20level%20of%20success%2C%20where%20we've%20grown%20to%20reasonably%20expect%20flawless%20execution%20each%20time%2C%20akin%20to%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20reliability%20and%20availability%20seen%20in%20sectors%20like%20telecommunications%20and%20cloud%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20critique%20of%20Lyft%20at%20all.%20Their%20mistake%20was%20a%20very%20big%20one%2C%20but%20it's%20surprising%20it%20doesn't%20happen%20more%20often%20to%20other%20companies.%20That's%20why%20this%20Lyft%20example%20stands%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20when%20you're%20in%20the%20boiler%20room%20on%20an%20earnings%20cycle%2C%20it%20often%20doesn't%20feel%20so%20smooth.%20Humans%20are%2C%20well%2C%20human%2C%20and%20mistakes%20get%20made.%20It%20occasionally%20feels%20like%20important%20balls%20are%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20being%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20%E2%80%94%20coming%20from%20somebody%20who's%20been%20around%20the%20earnings%20block%20a%20few%20times%20%E2%80%94%20here%20are%20my%20three%20suggestions%20for%20anybody%20playing%20a%20leadership%20role%20in%20any%20earnings%20process%2C%20all%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20helping%20your%20company%20avoid%20becoming%20a%20meme%20on%20this%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Obsess%20over%20the%20process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20something%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20swing%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20value%2C%20it's%20astonishing%20how%20rarely%20companies%20examine%20their%20internal%20systems%20driving%20an%20earnings%20report.%20Instead%2C%20that%20process%20often%20unfolds%20organically%20based%20on%20habit%2C%20and%20too%20often%2C%20it's%20little%20more%20than%20a%20basic%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarnings%20should%20be%20reviewed%20like%20any%20critical%20system%2C%20rigorously%20examined%20with%20a%20bird's-eye%20view%20of%20who%20does%20what%2C%20when%2C%20why%2C%20and%20how.%20This%20is%20especially%20necessary%20given%20how%20frequently%20executives%20and%20contributors%20can%20change%20in%20an%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%3A%20I%20always%20encourage%20companies%20to%20take%20a%20comprehensive%20look%20at%20their%20entire%20earnings%20system%20down%20to%20exquisite%20detail%