It%20has%20ordered%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20furnish%20details%20on%20donations%20and%20the%20political%20parties%20which%20received%20them%2C%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20has%20to%20publish%20the%20numbers%20by%20March%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20only%20indication%20of%20how%20much%20political%20parties%20have%20made%20from%20electoral%20bond%20donations%20are%20the%20amounts%20declared%20by%20the%20parties%20themselves%20in%20their%20Annual%20Audit%20Reports%20submitted%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20%E2%80%93%20part%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20which%20pronounced%20the%20quashing%20verdict%20today%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiveLawIndia%2Fstatus%2F1758077322752844056%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ecited%20these%20figures%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20separate%20but%20concurring%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20figures%2C%20compiled%20by%20Commonwealth%20Human%20Rights%20Initiative%20director%20Venkatesh%20Nayak%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20EC%E2%80%99s%20website%20and%20reports%20published%20by%20the%20Association%20of%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20reflect%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20significant%20and%20towering%20gains%20from%20a%20scheme%20now%20deemed%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20right%20to%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFigures%20filed%20by%20several%20parties%20are%20incomplete%20for%20certain%20years%20or%20unpublished%20on%20the%20EC%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20reflecting%20the%20opaque%20nature%20of%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20are%20a%20few%20charts%20that%20can%20help%20visualise%20the%20cash%20that%20flowed%20through%20political%20parties%20thanks%20to%20the%20scheme%20in%20the%20last%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20parties%20who%20filed%20the%20plea%20against%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20and%20did%20not%20accept%20donations%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%20It%20has%20thus%20not%20been%20included%20in%20any%20of%20the%20national%20or%20all-party%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F16815197%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F16814852%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F16814852%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F16814852%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F16815728%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F16815728%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F16815728%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F16815865%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F16815865%2F%3Futm_s