igure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20the%20venture%20is%20reaching%20a%20point%20where%20donations%20sometimes%20exceed%20the%20demand%20in%20a%20certain%20country%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20instance%2C%20during%20Chinese%20New%20Year%E2%80%9D%2C%20Anushka%20is%20exploring%20her%20options%20of%20starting%20cross-border%20donations.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20there%20are%20many%20nitty-gritty%20to%20take%20care%20of%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20her%20time%20of%20being%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20an%20idea%20that%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337729%2Fbihar-bamboo-startup-entrepreneur-satyam-sundaram-eco-friendly-products-profits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echampioning%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20society%2C%20Anushka%20says%20the%20lessons%20have%20been%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20realise%20how%20the%20motivation%20to%20donate%20differs%20as%20we%20shift%20time%20zones.%20In%20some%20places%2C%20it%20is%20driven%20by%20emotion%20or%20altruism%2C%20while%20in%20others%20it%20is%20driven%20by%20the%20need%20to%20become%20sustainable.%20But%20the%20willingness%20to%20%E2%80%98share%E2%80%99%20is%20what%20unites%20people%20from%20across%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708001385000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG-20240215-WA0020-1707998597.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341906%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Started%20by%20Anushka%20Jain%2C%20%E2%80%98Share%20At%20Door%20Step%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20social%20venture%20that%20simplifies%20the%20donation%20process.%20It%20collects%20clothes%2C%20toys%2C%20books%20and%20more%20from%20your%20doorstep%2C%20using%20AI%20to%20connect%20with%20NGOs%20throughout%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341906%2Fwhere-to-donate-clothes-books-toys-anushka-jain-share-at-door-step-ngos-artificial-intelligence%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Karnataka%20Is%20Delivering%20Rations%20to%20People%20Aged%2090%20and%20Above%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15174327%2FScreenshot-2024-02-15-at-5.43.16-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengaluru%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Revamma%2C%2094%2C%20stays%20alone%20in%20her%20two-room%20house%20in%20Kethohalli%20village%20in%20Ramanagar%2C%2030%20km%20south-west%20of%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20capital%20city.%20She%20can%20barely%20walk%20as%20her%20left%20leg%20is%20swollen%20due%20to%20an%20injury.%20Previously%2C%20she%20relied%20on%20her%20only%20daughter%20Manjula%2C%2056%2C%20to%20collect%20her%20rations%20from%20the%20government%20fair-price%20shop%20(FPS).%20An%20initiative%20launched%20last%20October%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20Food%20and%20Civil%20Supplies%20and%20Consumer%20Affairs%20Department%20ensures%20that%20she%20gets%205%20kg%20foodgrain%20at%20her%20doorstep%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%20(PDS)%2C%20either%20the%20fingerprint%20of%20the%20ration%20card%20holder%20is%20scanned%20or%20a%20one-time%20password%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20linked%20phone%20number%20to%20confirm%20delivery%20of%20foodgrain.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20is%20a%20daily%20wage%20worker.%20Once%20a%20month%2C%20after%20coming%20from%20work%20she%20used%20to%20collect%20my%20rations%20and%20give%20them%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Revamma.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20grateful%20that%20I%20directly%20get%20them%20at%20home.%20I%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20move%20around%20in%20my%20house%E2%80%93how%20could%20I%20go%20to%20the%20ration%20shop%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Anna%20Suvidha%E2%80%99%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fanna-suvidha-home-delivery-of-rice-to-elderly-beneficiaries%2Farticle67503899.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estarted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20Siddaramaiah-led%20Congress%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20to%20deliver%20rations%20to%20people%20who%20are%20aged%2090%20years%20and%20above.%20At%20present%2C%20single-member%20household%20Antodaya%20Anna%20Yojana%20(AAY)%20and%20Priority%20Household%20(PHH)%20ration%20card%20holders%20aged%2090%20years%20and%20above%20are%20entitled%20to%20receive%20the%20benefit.%20Each%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnfsa.gov.in%2Fportal%2FCoverage_Entitlements_NFSA_AA%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epriority%20household%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20beneficiary%20under%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnfsa.gov.in%2Fportal%2Fnfsa-act%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENational%20Food%20Security%20Act%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20provided%20with%205%20kg%20of%20foodgrain%2C%20and%20the%20poorest%20of%20the%20poor%20(AAY)%20households%20get%2035%20kg%20for%20free%20as%20NFSA%20entitlements.%20Priority%20households%20under%20NFSA%20are%20those%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fdownload_audit_report%2F2016%2FUnion_Civil_National_Food_Security_Report_54_of_2015.pdf%23page%3D5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eidentified%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20states%E2%80%99%20scheme%20guidelines%2C%20while%20AAY%20beneficiaries%20are%20based%20on%20scheme%20guidelines%20issued%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%205%2C314%20eligible%20individuals%20in%20the%20state%20as%20of%20February%202024%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Karnataka%20Food%20and%20Civil%20Supplies%20and%20Consumer%20Affairs%20Department.%20The%20FPS%20dealers%20deliver%20the%20rations%20every%20month%20to%20the%20recipients%2C%20and%20department%20officials%20use%20an%20app%20to%20track%20the%20status%20of%20the%20delivery.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESenior%20citizens%2C%20especially%20those%20aged%2090%20and%20above%2C%20found%20it%20near%20impossible%20to%20access%20ration%20shops%20and%20carry%20the%20provisions%20back%20home.%20The%20situation%20is%20harder%20for%20single-member%20households%2C%20i.e.%20those%20who%20do%20not%20live%20with%20their%20families%20due%20to%20factors%20such%20as%20perceived%20burden%2C%20poverty%2C%20low%20family%20income%2C%20migration%20of%20family%20members%20for%20work%2C%20or%20internal%20conflicts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20food%20security%20is%20the%20primary%20motive%2C%20it%20also%20brings%20hope%20and%20dignity%20back%20into%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20twilight%20years.%20%E2%80%9CA%20report%20published%20in%20a%20local%20newspaper%20%5Bin%20June%202022%5D%20highlighted%20how%20an%20old%20lady%20in%20Karwar%20was%20not%20able%20to%20carry%20the%20government-provided%20rations%20and%20almost%20starved%20for%20a%20few%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gyanendra%20Gangwar%2C%20former%20Additional%20Director%2C%20IT%20and%20Vigilance%2C%20Food%20and%20Civil%20Services%20Department.%20%E2%80%9COur%20food%20inspector%20personally%20visited%20her%20and%20provided%20her%20rations.%20This%20incident%20made%20us%20think%20that%20there%20will%20be%20many%20such%20individuals%20in%20the%20state%20who%20would%20need%20support.%20This%20is%20when%20we%20started%20conceptualising%20and%20analysing%20data%20for%20%E2%80%98Anna%20Suvidha%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20initiative%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20pilot%20stage%2C%20was%20started%20under%20Gangwar%E2%80%99s%20supervision.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20took%20the%20decision%20to%20sort%20the%20available%20data%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis%2C%20since%20many%20names%20get%20deleted%20due%20to%20deaths%20and%20new%20names%20are%20added%20as%20people%20are%20ageing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20beneficiaries%20were%20identified%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20February%202023%2C%20the%20Food%20and%20Civil%20Supplies%20Department%20initiated%20the%20process%20of%20sorting%20the%20digitally%20available%20ration%20card%20data%20to%20shortlist%20single-member%20households%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20age%E2%80%9370-79%2C%2080-89%2C%2090%20and%20above%2C%20and%20the%20various%20categories%20of%20cards%20(AAY%2C%20PHH%20and%20non-priority%20households)%2C%20according%20to%20Gangwar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENext%2C%20the%20food%20inspectors%20in%20different%20districts%20across%20the%20state%20were%20asked%20to%20physically%20verify%20details%20such%20as%20the%20address%20and%20contact%20details%20of%20nonagenarian%20and%20centenarian%20single-member%20AAY%20and%20PHH%20ration%20card%20holders%20by%20random%20sampling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20this%20physical%20verification%20process%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20many%20of%20the%20individuals%20whose%20names%20were%20in%20the%20list%20were%20dead.%20The%20department%20deleted%20the%20invalid%20ration%20cards%20from%20the%20database%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ee-janma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(birth%20and%20death%20registration)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fejanma.karnataka.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eportal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20data.%20After%20this%20exercise%2C%20the%20number%20of%20single%20member%20ration%20card%20householders%20in%20the%20state%20who%20were%2090%20and%20above%20in%20the%20AAY%20and%20PHH%20categories%20were%20found%20to%20be%20248%20and%208%2C066%2C%20respectively%2C%20Gangwar%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20an%20in-depth%20analysis%20of%20the%20ration%20uptake%20or%20collection%20status%20undertaken%20by%20the%20department%20found%20that%20there%20were%2037%25%20of%20single%20member%20households%20with%20AAY%20and%20PHH%20cards%20in%20this%20selected%20age%20bracket%20consistently%20missing%20their%20rations%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis%2C%20and%2024%25%20had%20not%20collected%20them%20for%20a%20continuous%20period%20of%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Devanahalli%20in%20Bengaluru%20Rural%2C%20Annamma%20(she%20uses%20one%20name)%2C%2090%20got%20her%20rations%20collected%20through%20her%20son%20L.%20Srinivas%2C%2049%2C%20and%20daughter-in-law%20Shobha%20Annayappa%2C%2039%2C%20only%20when%20they%20were%20free%20from%20work.%20She%20could%20not%20collect%20her%20rations%20in%20the%20month%20of%20September%202023%2C%20and%20was%20glad%20when%20the%20dealer%20delivered%20her%203%20kg%20rice%20and%202%20kg%20ragi%20in%20October%20when%20the%20initiative%20was%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20son%20is%20a%20mason%2C%E2%80%9D%20Annamma%20said.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20often%20goes%20out%20for%20work%20and%20does%20not%20return%20home%20for%20months.%20My%20daughter-in-law%20also%20accompanies%20him%20sometimes%20along%20with%20the%20kid.%20Previously%2C%20I%20used%20to%20wait%20for%20them%20to%20bring%20my%20rations%20and%20sometimes%20missed%20them%20when%20they%20were%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15174306%2FScreenshot-2024-02-15-at-5.42.09-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22978%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15174306%2FScreenshot-2024-02-15-at-5.42.09-PM.png%20978w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15174306%2FScreenshot-2024-02-15-at-5.42.09-PM-300x220.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697353%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22718%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAnnamma%2C%2090%20depended%20on%20her%20son%20and%20daughter-in-law%2C%20who%20often%20migrate%20in%20search%20of%20work%2C%20to%20collect%20her%20rations.%20She%20was%20glad%20when%20the%20fair-price%20shop%20dealer%20delivered%20her%203%20kg%20rice%20and%202%20kg%20ragi%20in%20October%202023%2C%20she%20says.%20Photo%3A%20Tamanna%20Naseer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETech-enabled%20collaboration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20requires%20collaboration%20between%20FPS%20dealers%2C%20food%20inspectors%2C%20and%20joint%20directors%2Fdeputy%20directors%20of%20the%20Food%20and%20Civil%20Supplies%20Department.%20For%20ensuring%20a%20smooth%20operational%20workflow%20and%20monitoring%20the%20process%2C%20a%20user-friendly%20mobile%20application%20was%20developed%20with%20the%20assistance%20of%20private%20software%20developers.%20This%20app%2C%20called%20%E2%80%98Anna%20Suvidha%E2%80%99%2C%20uses%20geo-tagging%20to%20verify%20the%20location%20of%20the%20delivery%3B%20hence%2C%20inspection%20can%20be%20done%20only%20at%20the%20location%20of%20the%20recipient%20where%20the%20rations%20are%20delivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interface%20of%20the%20app%20is%20slightly%20different%20for%20the%20FPS%20dealers%20and%20food%20inspectors.%20Once%20the%20head%20office%20in%20Bengaluru%20uploads%20the%20verified%20data%20in%20the%20server%20every%20month%2C%20food%20inspectors%20can%20view%20the%20number%20of%20recipients%20in%20their%20area%2C%20and%20the%20FPS%20dealers%20see%20the%20list%20of%20people%20to%20whom%20they%20have%20to%20home-deliver%20rations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFPS%20dealers%20have%20to%20take%20a%20photograph%20while%20delivering%20the%20foodgrain%20and%20upload%20it%20on%20the%20app.%20To%20ensure%20that%20the%20rations%20have%20been%20delivered%20by%20the%20dealer%2C%20food%20inspectors%20are%20required%20to%20visit%20some%20of%20the%20recipients%20and%20upload%20an%20image%20of%20inspection.%20When%20deliveries%20are%20not%20done%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20the%20names%20appear%20under%20%E2%80%98pending%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assistant%20programmers%E2%80%93who%20are%20contractual%20technical%20employees%E2%80%93of%20every%20district%20were%20provided%20virtual%20training%20in%20August%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20app.%20They%20trained%20the%20food%20inspectors%20who%20in%20turn%20explained%20the%20process%20to%20FPS%20dealers%20operating%20within%20their%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFair%20price%20shop%20dealers%20seek%20incentives%2C%20food%20inspectors%20struggle%20to%20verify%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20children%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20house%20after%20their%20marriage.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20really%20care%20for%20us.%20When%20we%20need%20help%2C%20our%20neighbours%20come%20to%20our%20rescue%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashwatha%20Bai%2C%2085%20said.%20They%20have%20four%20sons%20and%20one%20daughter.%20While%20she%20is%20a%20homemaker%2C%20her%20husband%20Narayan%20Rao%2C%2094%20is%20a%20tailor.%20He%20stopped%20working%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20due%20to%20knee%20pain.%20They%20live%20in%20Kengeri%20in%20Bengaluru%20Urban%2C%20and%20depend%20on%20financial%20assistance%20provided%20by%20the%20government%20for%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20poor%20health%2C%20the%20old%20couple%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20walk%20to%20the%20closest%20FPS%20which%20is%20a%20mere%20500%20metres%20away.%20%E2%80%9CPreviously%2C%20we%20asked%20our%20neighbour%20to%20bring%20our%20rations.%20We%20are%20very%20happy%20that%20the%20dealer%20comes%20home%20now.%20It%20is%20a%20great%20relief.%20May%20God%20bless%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rao%20said%2C%20as%20his%20eyes%20welled%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20ration%20card%20is%20in%20Ashwatha%20Bai%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20they%20still%20receive%20the%20rations%20at%20their%20doorstep%20since%20October%20as%20Rao%20is%20a%20nonagenarian.%20The%20department%20officials%20could%20not%20provide%20a%20satisfactory%20explanation%20of%20why%20the%20couple%20is%20considered%20for%20the%20home%20delivery%20initiative%20when%20it%20only%20covers%20single-member%20AAY%20and%20PHH%20card%20holders%20in%20the%2090%20and%20above%20age%20group.%20They%2C%20however%2C%20accepted%20that%20despite%20their%20best%20efforts%2C%20there%20are%20chances%20of%20discrepancies%20due%20to%20which%20a%20few%20people%20are%20probably%20left%20out%20from%20the%20database%20or%20some%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20meet%20the%20criteria%20are%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwatha%20Bai%20and%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20scenario%20reflects%20that%20couples%20in%20their%2080s%20and%2090s%20and%20single%20members%20in%20their%2080s%20will%20also%20largely%20benefit%20if%20they%20are%20brought%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20%E2%80%98Anna%20Suvidha%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20have%20to%20only%20take%20the%20rations%20to%20one%20house%20which%20is%20very%20close%20to%20my%20shop%2C%20I%20have%20no%20problem%20delivering%20it%20for%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shankaraiah%20K.S.%2C%2052%2C%20an%20FPS%20dealer%20in%20Kethohalli%20village%2C%20said.%20He%20wants%20the%20government%20to%20increase%20the%20incentive%20(currently%20Rs%20124%20per%20quintal)%20given%20to%20dealers%20for%20rations%20distributed%20under%20the%20PDS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ.L.%20Somashekar%2C%2040%2C%20who%20runs%20an%20FPS%20in%20Devanahalli%2C%20echoed%20this%20view.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20month%2C%20I%20pay%20Rs%204%2C000%20rent%20for%20the%20shop%20and%20Rs%204%2C000%20to%20the%20helper%20for%20offloading%20foodgrain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20pointed%20out.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20electricity%2C%20I%20have%20to%20shell%20out%20Rs%20250%20approximately%20and%20Rs%20300%20for%20internet.%20With%20all%20these%20expenses%2C%20it%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20manage%20the%20shop%20with%20such%20low%20incentive.%20For%20home%20delivery%2C%20I%20am%20currently%20providing%20rations%20to%20only%20one%20person.%20I%20will%20be%20happy%20if%20the%20government%20provides%20an%20extra%20amount%20for%20delivery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15174520%2FScreenshot-2024-02-15-at-5.44.28-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22977%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15174520%2FScreenshot-2024-02-15-at-5.44.28-PM.png%20977w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15174520%2FScreenshot-2024-02-15-at-5.44.28-PM-300x191.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697355%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22623%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJ.L.%20Somashekar%2C%20a%20fair-price%20shop%20dealer%20in%20Devanahalli%20in%20Bengaluru%20Rural.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20home%20delivery%2C%20I%20am%20currently%20providing%20rations%20to%20only%20one%20person.%20I%20will%20be%20happy%20if%20the%20government%20provides%20an%20extra%20amount%20for%20delivery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Photo%3A%20Tamanna%20Naseer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20report%20on%20strengthening%20PDS%20using%20technology%20in%20March%202021%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Food%2C%20Consumer%20Affairs%2C%20and%20Public%20Distribution%20recommended%20increasing%20the%20margin%20of%20FPSs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Food%20and%20Civil%20Supplies%20Department%20officials%20feel%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20incentivise%20the%20FPS%20dealers%20as%20it%20will%20keep%20them%20%E2%80%9Cmotivated%E2%80%9D.%20Raghu%20N.%2C%20Bengaluru%20Urban%20food%20inspector%2C%20suggested%20that%20the%20FPS%20dealers%20are%20%E2%80%9Clistening%E2%80%9D%20to%20them%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccomplying%E2%80%9D%20with%20their%20requests%20only%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20do%20doorstep%20delivery%20for%20more%20than%20one%20or%20two%20households%20at%20present.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20future%2C%20if%20we%20plan%20to%20add%20more%20people%20under%20the%20initiative%2C%20like%20the%20disabled%20category%2C%20then%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20expect%20services%20from%20dealers%20for%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Food%20and%20Civil%20Supplies%20and%20Consumer%20Affairs%20Department%2C%20the%20number%20of%20nonagenarians%20and%20centenarians%20who%20have%20received%20rations%20at%20home%20in%20October%2C%20November%2C%20December%20and%20January%20are%20788%2C%20667%2C%20521%20and%20456%2C%20respectively.%20This%20declining%20trend%20indicates%20that%20the%20assessment%20of%20the%20department%20officials%2C%20that%20the%20FPS%20dealers%20are%20not%20%E2%80%9Cmotivated%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20correct%20and%20the%20failure%20to%20provide%20financial%20incentive%20to%20FPS%20dealers%20is%20a%20real%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20use%20an%20app%20to%20implement%20and%20monitor%20%E2%80%98Anna%20Suvidha%E2%80%99%2C%20we%20know%20exactly%20how%20many%20deliveries%20are%20made%20and%20what%20is%20the%20status%20on%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Prathik%20G.%20Hegde%2C%20Assistant%20Director%2C%20Karnataka%20Food%20and%20Civil%20Supplies%20and%20Consumer%20Affairs%20Department.%20%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20the%20point%20is%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20push%20FPS%20dealers%20since%20we%20are%20not%20paying%20them%20any%20amount%20for%20home-delivering%20rations.%20Therefore%2C%20even%20when%20we%20are%20aware%20that%20some%20of%20the%20dealers%20are%20not%20complying%20with%20our%20requests%20at%20all%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20force%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20proposed%20to%20the%20Finance%20Department%20to%20consider%20allocating%20funds%20for%20this%20initiative%20in%20the%20state%20budget%20this%20year.%20If%20the%20budget%20announcement%20is%20made%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20provide%20Rs%2050%20as%20incentive%20to%20the%20FPS%20dealers%20for%20each%20delivery%20every%20month.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20important%20aspect%20is%20the%20verification%20undertaken%20by%20the%20food%20inspectors%20to%20confirm%20delivery.%20In%20Ramanagar%20district%2C%20to%20cover%20a%20distance%20of%2010%20km%20approximately%2C%20food%20inspector%20T.%20Nirmala%20travels%20in%20a%20bus%20for%20a%20few%20kilometres%20on%20the%20highway%20from%20her%20office%20and%20then%20waits%20for%20the%20FPS%20dealer%20to%20take%20her%20to%20Kethohalli%20village%20in%20his%20vehicle%3B%20there%20is%20one%20eligible%20recipient%20in%20this%20village.%20%E2%80%9COur%20department%20does%20not%20have%20vehicles%20to%20be%20taken%20for%20verifying%20home%20delivery%20of%20rations.%20We%20have%20to%20manage%20to%20reach%20the%20recipient%E2%80%99s%20house%20for%20monthly%20verification%20on%20our%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirmala%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Ramanagar%2C%20there%20are%2049%20FPS%20under%20my%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20this%20is%20the%20situation%20in%20Ramanagar%2C%20close%20to%20the%20state%20capital%2C%20food%20inspectors%20in%20remote%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20with%20scant%20coverage%20of%20public%20transport%20will%20have%20to%20struggle%20to%20go%20for%20verification%20drives%20under%20%E2%80%98Anna%20Suvidha%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETried%20and%20tested%20in%20other%20states%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDifferent%20doorstep%20ration%20delivery%20schemes%20were%20introduced%20in%20other%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20such%20as%20Kerala%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kerala%20government%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fin-other-news%2F140223%2Fkerala-civil-dept-to-deliver-ration-goods-through-auto-rickshaw.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elaunched%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20scheme%20called%20%E2%80%98OPPAM%E2%80%99%20on%20a%20pilot%20basis%20on%20February%2013%2C%202023%20in%20Nadathara%20Panchayat%20in%20Thrissur%20District.%20The%20Department%20of%20Food%2C%20Civil%20Supplies%20and%20Consumer%20Affairs%20and%20auto%20rickshaw%20employees%20collaborated%20to%20deliver%20foodgrain%20at%20the%20doorstep%20of%20extremely%20poor%20families%2C%20and%20impoverished%20and%20bedridden%20persons%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20later%20introduced%20in%20Kozhikode%20district%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20autorickshaw%20drivers%20don%E2%80%99t%20charge%20any%20money%20for%20participating%20in%20this%20free%20home%20delivery%20initiative.%20We%20have%20successfully%20launched%20it%20across%20the%20state%20and%20it%20is%20in%20every%20district%20of%20Kerala%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kerala%20Civil%20Supplies%20Commissioner%20D.%20Sajith%20Babu%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20beauty%20of%20our%20scheme%20is%20that%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20spend%20any%20additional%20amount.%20We%20have%20mapped%20the%20auto%20rickshaws%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20the%20auto%20drivers%20can%20take%20the%20rations%20with%20them%20after%20completing%20their%20work%20as%20the%20delivery%20locations%20are%20between%20the%20auto%20stands%20and%20their%20homes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20the%20department%20ensures%20that%20there%20is%20no%20leakage%2C%20Babu%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20recipients%20sign%20a%20receipt%20after%20receiving%20the%20rations.%20Additionally%2C%20our%20ration%20inspectors%20visit%20the%20houses%20of%20recipients%20for%20random%20checks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20scheme%20has%20sociological%20benefits.%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20this%20scheme%2C%20we%20provide%20rations%20to%20the%20extremely%20poor%20who%20are%20mostly%20old%2C%20disabled%20and%20sick.%20Many%20of%20them%20are%20living%20alone%20without%20any%20support.%20When%20the%20auto%20rickshaw%20drivers%20visit%20the%20houses%20of%20such%20people%20and%20find%20out%20that%20they%20need%20any%20help%20like%20medical%20attention%2C%20they%20inform%20the%20ASHA%20workers%20%5Baccredited%20social%20health%20activists%5D%20in%20the%20area.%20In%20this%20manner%2C%20the%20scheme%20is%20benefiting%20people%20in%20multiple%20ways.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Mukhyamantri%20Ghar%20Ghar%20Ration%20Yojana%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fkeeping-pre-poll-promise-kejriwal-announces-ration-at-the-doorstep-6517265%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elaunched%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20in%20Delhi%20aimed%20to%20deliver%20packed%20rations%E2%80%93wheat%20flour%2C%20rice%20and%20sugar%E2%80%93under%20the%20Targeted%20Public%20Distribution%20System%20(TPDS)%20to%207.2%20million%20people%20in%20the%20capital%20who%20were%20eligible%20for%20PDS%20after%20biometric%20verification%20through%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fpti-stories%2Fimplement-epos-enabled-doorstep-delivery-of-ration-across-country-hussain-to-centre-119020501305_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ee-POS%20method%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20never%20implemented%20and%20remained%20only%20on%20paper%20since%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-hc-sets-aside-doorstep-ration-delivery-scheme-101653002877599.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Escrapped%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20scheme.%20The%20Delhi%20Sarkari%20Ration%20Dealers%20Sangh%2C%20a%20group%20of%20FPS%20owners%2C%20challenged%20it%20in%20court%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20door-to-door%20rations%20programme%20should%20be%20declared%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eultra%20vires%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(beyond%20one%E2%80%99s%20legal%20power%20or%20authority).%20The%20High%20Court%20bench%20underlined%20that%20the%20policy%20did%20not%20comply%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20(NFSA)%2C%202013%2C%20effectively%20ending%20its%20legality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20Punjab%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Fhc-stays-punjab-plan-for-ration-home-delivery%2Farticleshow%2F94545540.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efaced%20legal%20hurdles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20it%20launched%20the%20Ghar%20Ghar%20Ration%20Yojana%20since%20it%20was%20challenged%20by%20depot%20owners.%20They%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fdelhi-arvind-kejriwal-doorstep-free-ration-delivery-scheme-punjab-bhagwant-mann-2500247-2024-02-11%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erelaunched%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20it%20on%20February%2010%2C%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20door-to-door%20delivery%20of%20food%20grains%20under%20PDS%20is%20a%20good%20idea%20for%20people%20above%2090%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Siraj%20Hussain%2C%20former%20Union%20secretary%20for%20agriculture.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20doorstep%20delivery%20of%20rations%20is%20done%2C%20then%20grains%20like%20wheat%20should%20not%20be%20given%20which%20cannot%20be%20readily%20cooked.%20How%20can%20they%20go%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echakki%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20then%20get%20it%20converted%20into%20flour%3F%20It%20is%20a%20good%20thing%20that%20Karnataka%20is%20giving%20rice%20which%20can%20be%20cooked%20directly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hussain%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20concerns%20related%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20rice%2C%20jawar%20and%20ragi%20home-delivered%20by%20the%20FPS%20dealers%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20evaluation%20done%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farcusresearch.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArcus%20Policy%20Research%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20suggests%20that%20more%20people%20in%20urban%20areas%20are%20satisfied%20with%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20PDS%20than%20the%20people%20in%20rural%20areas.%20Generally%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20rice%20issued%20by%20the%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%20is%20good.%20So%20quality%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20an%20issue%20as%20such%20in%20the%20state%20in%20general.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20way%20forward%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20ration%20shop%20dealers%20resort%20to%20malpractices%2C%20illegal%20diversions%20of%20commodities%2C%20holding%20and%20black%20marketing%20due%20to%20the%20minimum%20salary%20received%20by%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20this%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldwidejournals.com%2Fparipex%2Frecent_issues_pdf%2F2017%2FMarch%2Fcorruption-in-public-distribution-system_March_2017_6796818214_6812638.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eresearch%20paper%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20%E2%80%98Corruption%20in%20Public%20Distribution%20System%E2%80%99.%20Further%2C%20the%20paper%20said%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9CFPS%20dealers%20indulge%20in%20malpractices%20in%20inappropriate%20weighting%20of%20the%20materials%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F44002966%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eresearch%20work%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20%E2%80%98Does%20Computerisation%20reduce%20PDS%20Leakage%20%E2%80%93%20Lessons%20from%20Karnataka%E2%80%99%20conducted%20by%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%20fellow%20Silvia%20Masiero%2C%20it%20was%20underlined%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpolicy%20shifts%20cannot%20be%20achieved%20by%20technology%20alone%E2%80%9D.%20It%20holds%20true%20for%20the%20home%20delivery%20initiative%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20very%20essence%20of%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20(NFSA)%20is%20to%20guarantee%20food%20security%20to%20every%20individual%2C%20ensuring%20that%20even%20the%20last%20person%20in%20the%20queue%20is%20not%20deprived.%20In%20the%20context%20of%20this%20initiative%2C%20an%20elderly%20AAY%20or%20PHH%20cardholder%20not%20only%20occupies%20the%20position%20of%20the%20last%20member%20but%20also%20represents%20the%20most%20vulnerable.%20The%20over-reliance%20on%20FPS%20dealers%2C%20however%2C%20without%20or%20even%20with%20financial%20incentive%2C%20might%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20hurdle%20for%20the%20overall%20success%20of%20the%20programme%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20doubt%20this%20is%20an%20experiment%20worth%20watching%2C%E2%80%9D%20economist%20Jean%20Dreze%20told%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CFood%20grain%20rations%20are%20quite%20bulky%20and%20they%20can%20be%20difficult%20for%20elderly%20or%20disabled%20persons%20to%20manage%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20live%20alone%20and%20far%20away%20from%20the%20distribution%20point.%20The%20question%20is%20whether%20there%20is%20a%20practical%20and%20reliable%20way%20of%20taking%20the%20rations%20to%20their%20doorstep.%20The%20proof%20of%20the%20pudding%20will%20be%20in%20the%20delivery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThis%20story%20was%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fgovernance%2Fhow-karnataka-is-delivering-rations-to-people-aged-90-above-894937%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2F%5C%22%3EIndiaSpend%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20data-driven%2C%20public-interest%20journalism%20non-profit.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708000218000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15174327%2FScreenshot-2024-02-15-at-5.43.16-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-karnataka-is-delivering-rations-to-people-aged-90-and-above%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Through%20Anna%20Suvidha%2C%20launched%20in%20October%202023%2C%20the%20government%20is%20delivering%20rations%20to%20the%20doorstep%20of%20nonagenarians%20and%20centenarians%20living%20alone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-karnataka-is-delivering-rations-to-people-aged-90-and-above%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cloud%20Over%20INDIA%20Bloc%20as%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20Says%20National%20Conference%20Will%20Go%20it%20Alone%20in%20LS%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F27150709%2F2212-KT-Farooq.00_48_22_13.Still033-1-e1707997880327.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20National%20Conference%20supremo%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20has%20said%20that%20his%20party%20will%20contest%20alone%20on%20all%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20in%20what%20may%20prove%20to%20be%20yet%20another%20setback%20for%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbdullah%20also%20hinted%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20simultaneous%20assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Political%20parties%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20have%20been%20demanding%20an%20assembly%20election%20ever%20since%20Article%20370%20was%20read%20down.%20The%20Union%20government%20has%20been%20reluctant%20in%20conducting%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20seat%20sharing%20is%20concerned%2C%20I%20want%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20the%20National%20Conference%20will%20contest%20elections%20on%20its%20own%20strength.%20There%20are%20no%20two%20opinions%20about%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20should%20be%20no%20questions%20on%20this%20anymore%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20Abdullah%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20elections%20in%20both%20states%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20will%20be%20held%20with%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbdullah%E2%80%99s%20decision%20has%20come%20after%20a%20number%20of%20his%20party%20leaders%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%20joined%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20last%20month.%20The%20delay%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks%20may%20have%20triggered%20the%20announcement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2012%2C%20Abdullah%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fed-summons-farooq-abdullah-for-questioning-in-money-laundering-case-101707748254275.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esummoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20questioning%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20alleged%20financial%20irregularities%20in%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Cricket%20Association.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20veteran%20Kashmir%20leader%20did%20not%20rule%20out%20returning%20to%20the%20NDA%20fold%20in%20the%20future.%20Abdullah%20had%20expressed%20his%20anguish%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%2C%20and%20had%20hinted%20at%20forming%20a%20separate%20alliance%20in%20Kashmir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20chief%20spokesperson%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20responded%20to%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETalks%20are%20going%20on.%20Every%20party%20has%20their%20own%20limitations.%20National%20Conference%20and%20PDP%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20remain%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbdullah%E2%80%99s%20flip-flop%20may%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20as%20he%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20advocates%20of%20forming%20a%20united%20opposition%20alliance.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20opponents%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20recent%20times.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20Abdullah%20asserted%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cto%20safeguard%20the%20nation%2C%20we%20must%20set%20aside%20our%20disagreements%20and%20prioritise%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20welfare.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20unlike%20his%20father%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fomar-abdullah-national-conference-india-bloc-farooq-abdullah-2024-lok-sabha-elections-2502699-2024-02-15%5C%22%3Easserted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20National%20Conference%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarooq%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20son%20and%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20said%20that%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20statement%20was%20a%20reflection%20of%20what%20the%20party%20cadre%20feels%20but%20indicated%20that%20the%20NC%E2%80%99s%20talks%20with%20Congress%20and%20PDP%20may%20have%20hit%20a%20roadblock%20over%20its%20interest%20in%20contesting%20a%20few%20seats%20where%20other%20INDIA%20constituents%20in%20the%20valley%20too%20want%20to%20field%20their%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20seat%20sharing%2C%20we%20have%20been%20very%20clear%20for%20the%20last%20few%20months.%20The%20seats%20that%20will%20be%20discussed%20are%20those%20that%20are%20held%20with%20BJP%2C%20we%20are%20firm%20on%20that%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNational%20Conference%20has%20made%20no%20secrets%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20would%20rather%20fight%20elections%20on%20all%20seats%2C%20but%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20sometimes%20for%20a%20bigger%20objective%2C%20small%20sacrifices%20have%20to%20be%20made.%20If%20the%20bigger%20objective%20is%20to%20win%20seats%20back%20from%20the%20BJP%E2%80%A6then%20if%20it%20is%20necessary%20for%20NC%20to%20enter%20into%20seat%20sharing%20with%20Congress%2C%20our%20doors%20are%20open%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20yet%20had%20any%20formal%20discussion%20with%20Congress%20(on%20seat%20sharing)%2C%20informally%20some%20dialogues%20have%20taken%20place.%20We%20are%20not%20the%20sort%20of%20a%20party%20that%20has%20our%20feet%20in%20multiple%20boats%2C%20once%20we%20make%20friends%2C%20we%20stick%20to%20those%20friends%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20recently%20left%20the%20alliance%20and%20joined%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance.%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20also%20exited%20INDIA%20after%20she%20declared%20that%20she%20will%20contest%20alone%20in%20West%20Bengal%20after%20her%20party%E2%80%99s%20talks%20with%20the%20Congress%20on%20seat-sharing%20collapsed.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20chief%20minister%20in%20Punjab%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20has%20also%20said%20that%20the%20party%20will%20contest%20all%2013%20seats%20in%20Punjab%2C%20leaving%20the%20Congress%20embarrassed.%20More%20recently%2C%20the%20talks%20between%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20also%20appear%20to%20be%20crashing%20after%20AAP%20only%20agreed%20to%20vacate%20one%20of%20the%20seven%20seats%20of%20Delhi%20for%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707997898000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F27150709%2F2212-KT-Farooq.00_48_22_13.Still033-1-e1707997880327.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcloud-over-india-bloc-as-farooq-abdullah-says-national-conference-will-go-it-alone%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Significantly%2C%20the%20veteran%20Kashmir%20leader%20who%20had%20been%20one%20of%20the%20main%20votaries%20of%20a%20united%20anti-NDA%20force%2C%20did%20not%20rule%20out%20returning%20to%20the%20NDA%20in%20the%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcloud-over-india-bloc-as-farooq-abdullah-says-national-conference-will-go-it-alone%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20has%20signalled%20space%20arms%20race%20is%20on%20-%20with%20enormous%20risks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707996900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-vladimir-putin-russia_6456400.jpg%3F20240215114828%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frussia-has-signalled-that-the-space-arms-race-is-on-with-enormous-risks-13072140%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20is%20secretly%20developing%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20satellite-killing%20space%20weapon%2C%20according%20to%20US%20intelligence%20watchdogs%20in%20Washington.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A377%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frussia-has-signalled-that-the-space-arms-race-is-on-with-enormous-risks-13072140%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Frussia-has-signalled-that-the-space-arms-race-is-on-with-enormous-risks-13072140%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Frussia-has-signalled-that-the-space-arms-race-is-on-with-enormous-risks-13072140%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Planetary%20Perspective%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15155616%2FPandavFalls06.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20article%20in%20a%20series%20about%20the%20Earth-system%20%E2%80%93%20how%20our%20planet%20has%20shaped%20us%20as%20human%20beings%2C%20and%20how%20we%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20have%20shaped%20it.%20Read%20the%20series%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fearths-changing-climate%5C%22%3EPart%201%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20on%20a%20madly%20unstable%20planet.%20For%20billions%20of%20years%20it%20has%20never%20stopped%20wobbling%20and%20wandering%2C%20freezing%20and%20thawing%2C%20cracking%20and%20flowing%2C%20blooming%2C%20dying%2C%20regenerating.%20Small%20changes%20in%20its%20chemical%20composition%2C%20geological%20cycling%2C%20orbit%2C%20or%20orientation%20in%20space%20cascade%20into%20extreme%20changes%20felt%20on%20its%20surface.%20Despite%20this%E2%80%94maybe%20because%20of%20it%E2%80%94our%20planet%20has%20also%20given%20birth%20to%20a%20complex%2C%20interwoven%2C%20and%20forever%20changing%20family%20of%20living%20beings%2C%20a%20rarity%20in%20the%20cosmos%20as%20far%20as%20we%20know.%20Understanding%20this%20bigger%20picture%20of%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20planet%20itself%20and%20human%20life%20can%20help%20us%20gain%20some%20perspective%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fearths-changing-climate%5C%22%3Eour%20modern%20predicament%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20let%E2%80%99s%20begin%20at%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896.jpg%20874w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896-219x300.jpg%20219w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896-746x1024.jpg%20746w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696598%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22412%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarth%20was%20born%20about%20four%20and%20a%20half%20billion%20years%20ago%2C%20alongside%20several%20sibling%20planets%2C%20all%20of%20them%20formed%20from%20fragments%20of%20material%20left%20over%20after%20the%20birth%20of%20the%20Sun.%20It%20began%20as%20a%20glob%20of%20fiery%2C%20fluid%20rock%20spinning%20amidst%20other%20bits%20of%20ice%20and%20stone.%20But%20over%20the%20course%20of%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20first%20half%20billion%20years%2C%20its%20molten%20surface%20cooled%20and%20solidified%3B%20its%20dry%2C%20sulfurous%20skies%20became%20unending%20showers%20of%20acid%20rain%3B%20its%20empty%20basins%20filled%20with%20water.%20In%20these%20new%20oceans%20simmered%20a%20rich%20elemental%20brew%20of%20carbon%2C%20hydrogen%2C%20nitrogen%2C%20phosphorous%2C%20iron%E2%80%94to%20mention%20but%20a%20few%20star%20ingredients%E2%80%94absorbing%20heat-energy%20from%20deep-sea%20hydrothermal%20vents%20and%20joining%20together%20into%20chains%20of%20chemicals.%20These%20complex%20molecules%20then%20clustered%20together%2C%20generating%20higher%20order%20structures%2C%20eventually%20forming%20cells%20that%20ate%20and%20breathed%20and%20reproduced%E2%80%94living%20avatars%20of%20dust%2C%20born%20of%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20own%20dynamically%20interconnected%20biological%2C%20geological%2C%20and%20chemical%20processes%2C%20or%20%3Cem%3Ebiogeochemistry%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20earliest%20lifeforms%20were%20coming%20into%20being%2C%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20surface%20was%20still%20being%20relentlessly%20pummelled%20by%20meteors%2C%20some%20of%20them%20the%20size%20of%20mountains.%20Great%20impacts%20injected%20new%20material%20into%20our%20planet%2C%20cracking%20and%20reshaping%20its%20biogeochemistry.%20In%20this%20environment%2C%20about%203.5%20billion%20years%20ago%2C%20some%20of%20those%20early%20cells%20evolved%20a%20new%20ability%20to%20convert%20light-energy%20from%20the%20sun%20into%20chemical%20fuel%20through%20a%20process%2C%20called%20%3Cem%3Ephotosynthesis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20takes%20carbon-dioxide%20from%20the%20air%20and%20emits%20oxygen%20as%20metabolic%20waste.%20By%20two%20billion%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20buildup%20of%20oxygen%20was%20turning%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20skies%20blue%20above%20its%20oceans%20of%20rust-red.%20Many%20forms%20of%20life%20in%20that%20nascent%20biosphere%20were%20poisoned%20by%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fslate.com%2Ftechnology%2F2014%2F07%2Fthe-great-oxygenation-event-the-earths-first-mass-extinction.html%5C%22%3Eatmospheric%20oxygen%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20went%20extinct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3ECoal%20beds%20found%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mlsu.ac.in%2Fecontents%2F1895_Distribution%252520of%252520Coal%252520%26amp%3B%252520Petroleum%252520in%252520India.pdf%5C%22%3Epeninsular%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20the%20remains%20of%20swamp%20forests%20that%20bloomed%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffossil.energy.gov%2Finternational%2FPublications%2Fucg_1106_gsi.pdf%5C%22%3E290%20million%20years%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20supercontinent%20Pangea%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livescience.com%2F38218-facts-about-pangaea.html%5C%22%3Ein%20extreme%20southern%20latitudes%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20Earth%20was%20so%20hot%20that%20forests%20bloomed%20near%20Antarctica.%20But%20170%20million%20years%20later%2C%20the%20land%20containing%20those%20primeval%20forests%E2%80%94long%20since%20dead%20and%20buried%E2%80%94broke%20off%20as%20an%20island%20and%20floated%20northward.%20Its%20collision%20with%20the%20Eurasian%20landmass%20pushed%20up%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20highest%20mountains%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DA_K6LSSZ_34%5C%22%3Einducing%20the%20Indian%20monsoon%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20planet-wide%20cooling%20trend.%20Sixty%20million%20years%20later%2C%20the%20country%20south%20of%20the%20Himalayas%20would%20find%20itself%20rich%20with%20coal.%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20life%20itself%20was%20not%20defeated.%20The%20cells%20that%20did%20survive%20continued%20to%20diversify%20into%20myriad%20new%20forms%20that%20could%20withstand%20and%20even%20make%20use%20of%20this%20corrosive%20new%20gas.%20Some%20of%20these%20found%20ways%20to%20work%20together%2C%20joining%20into%20multicellular%20lifeforms%2C%20mixing%20genes%20through%20sexual%20reproduction%2C%20eventually%20filling%20the%20oceans%20with%20early%20forms%20of%20fungi%2C%20plants%2C%20and%20animals%20by%20around%20one%20billion%20years%20ago.%20These%20creatures%20grew%20and%20died%2C%20burrowed%20and%20crawled%2C%20built%20residual%20structures%2C%20stirred%20sediments%2C%20altered%20rocks%20and%20seabeds%20in%20ways%20that%20further%20changed%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20biogeochemistry.%20This%20changing%20geochemistry%20also%20affected%20the%20structure%20and%20motion%20of%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20crust%2C%20now%20sliding%20and%20tearing%2C%20bumping%20and%20churning%20up%20the%20landforms%20into%20barren%20mountains%20and%20valleys%20and%20volcanic%20alleys%2C%20exposing%20new%2C%20unweathered%20rock%E2%80%94which%20further%20changed%20biogeochemical%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20this%20lively%20flourishing%2C%20the%20changes%20led%20to%20the%20entire%20planet%20freezing%20over.%20By%20around%20720%20million%20years%20ago%2C%20floating%20icebergs%20and%20islands%20of%20slush%20were%20drif